title: Beautiful 3 bed plus Den 2 Bath Home For Rent
posting_body: ['Go to <URL> for instant access to all photos, details and more.', 'Beautiful Rental!', '\xa0 3 Bedroom plus Den and 2 Bathrooms.', '\xa0 Upgraded Hardwood Flooring, Gourmet Style Kitchen with Upgraded Counters and Cabinets, Stailless Steel stove, dishwasher, and microwave.', '\xa0 Large dining area adjacent to the kitchen and oversized Living Room with natural gas fireplace.', '\xa0 Den is perfect for home office or study area, Master bedroom has french doors to custom patio, and large master bathroom with soaking tub and custom tile shower, plus two walk in closets.', '\xa0 Additional bedrooms are large in size with good closet space.', '\xa0 Second bathroom has custom tile in the tub area, and upgraded vanity, faucet, sink, and lighting.', '\xa0 Nice back yard and 2 car garage.', '\xa0 Enjoy all the Savannah amenities including clubhouse, water park, pool, parks, ponds, and so much more.', '\xa0 Close proximity to shopping and great for commuting.', 'Troy Sage', 'Realtor', 'powered by eXp', 'show contact info', 'Office:', 'show contact info', 'Licensed', 'In: Tx, CA, AZ', 'License #: 0766375', 'Equal Housing Opportunity']
